The greatest super hero comic of all-time is finally here. WOLVERINE: ENEMY OF THE STATE&#039;s team of MARK MILLAR (CIVIL WAR) and JOHN ROMITA JR. Well, this is the book for you--the comic that starts where other super hero books draw the line. KICK-ASS is realistic super heroes taken to the next level. Miss out and you&#039;re an idiot!
